  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you lose hit points, you can use your reaction to enter a mystical trance-like state. During this state you gain +2 damage to attacks and resistance to bludgeoning, cutting, and piercing damage. Mortification ends at the end of the your next turn if you did not attack a hostile creature or suffered any damage in your last turn, or after one minute. This ability cannot be used again if you have not passed their turn without mortification before. If the flagellant has exhaustion levels, they can activate mortification at any time. Mortification cannot be used to reduce the cost of actions in a narrative sequence.</span> </p>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
